metadata.name: End Of Days
metadata.description:
This is one of the most important images that I've created by far. Not because it brought me worldwide recognition but because I made this image in a very hard and dark time that only love and passion could have forced me to get up every day and go out for a shoot.

Buyer will receive a physical piece on a museum quality paper at the size of 60"x40" inches as a gift.
Signed, Unframed.

Captured by digital camera in New York City, 
January 2014.
